    tester "Dou Qi, 3rd Stage!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:24
translate english ch1_s1_test_f1a282fc:

    # "望着测验魔石碑上面闪亮得甚至有些刺眼的五个大字，少年面无表情，唇角有着一抹自嘲，紧握的手掌，因为大力，而导致略微尖锐的指甲深深的刺进了掌心之中，带来一阵阵钻心的疼痛……"
    "Looking at the five large, shiny, almost blinding words on the Magic Testing Monolith, the boy remained expressionless, a trace of self-mockery on the corner of his lips. His tightly clenched fists, due to the force, caused his slightly sharp fingernails to dig deep into his palms, bringing waves of piercing pain..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:26
translate english ch1_s1_test_96b28408:

    # tester "萧炎，斗之力，三段！级别：低级！"
    tester "Xiao Yan, Dou Qi, 3rd Stage! Rank: Low!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:31
translate english ch1_s1_test_07c75072:

    # "中年男子话刚刚脱口，便是不出意外的在人头汹涌的广场上带起了一阵嘲讽的骚动。"
    "As soon as the middle-aged man finished speaking, it unsurprisingly stirred up a commotion of ridicule in the crowded square."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:33
translate english ch1_s1_test_a1e6468c:

    # crowd "三段？嘿嘿，果然不出我所料，这个‘天才’这一年又是在原地踏步！"
    crowd "3rd Stage? Hehe, just as I expected. This 'genius' has made no progress again this year!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:35
translate english ch1_s1_test_0864ec9d:

    # crowd "哎，这废物真是把家族的脸都给丢光了。"
    crowd "Sigh, this trash has really disgraced the clan completely."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:37
translate english ch1_s1_test_2dc418e2:

    # crowd "要不是族长是他的父亲，这种废物，早就被驱赶出家族，任其自生自灭了，哪还有机会待在家族中白吃白喝。"
    crowd "If the Clan Leader wasn't his father, this kind of trash would have been kicked out of the clan long ago to fend for himself. How would he still have the chance to stay in the clan, freeloading?"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:39
translate english ch1_s1_test_59ccaffa:

    # crowd "唉，昔年那名闻乌坦城的天才少年，如今怎么落魄成这般模样了啊？"
    crowd "Alas, the genius boy who was famous in Wu Tan City back then, how did he fall to such a state now?"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:41
translate english ch1_s1_test_d8e8ca9d:

    # crowd "谁知道呢，或许做了什么亏心事，惹得神灵降怒了吧……"
    crowd "Who knows? Maybe he did something against his conscience and angered the gods..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:43
translate english ch1_s1_test_0d22dd4d:

    # "周围传来的不屑嘲笑以及惋惜轻叹，落在那如木桩待在原地的少年耳中，恍如一根根利刺狠狠的扎在心脏一般，让得少年呼吸微微急促。"
    "The disdainful ridicule and regretful sighs from around fell into the ears of the boy who stood there like a wooden stake. They felt like sharp thorns stabbing fiercely into his heart, causing his breathing to become slightly rapid."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:48
translate english ch1_s1_test_12c7c05f:

    # "少年缓缓抬起头来，露出一张有些清秀的稚嫩脸庞，漆黑的眸子木然的在周围那些嘲讽的同龄人身上扫过，少年嘴角的自嘲，似乎变得更加苦涩了。"
    "The boy slowly raised his head, revealing a delicate and immature face. His pitch-black eyes numbly swept over the mocking peers around him, and the self-mockery at the corner of his mouth seemed to become even more bitter."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:50
translate english ch1_s1_test_7ec7a843:

    # xy "这些人，都如此刻薄势力吗？或许是因为三年前他们曾经在自己面前露出过最谦卑的笑容，所以，如今想要讨还回去吧……"
    xy "Are these people all so snobbish? Perhaps because three years ago they showed the most humble smiles in front of me, so now they want to take it back..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s1_test.rpy:55
translate english ch1_s1_test_9f7dfdc9:

    # "苦涩的一笑，萧炎落寞的转身，安静的回到了队伍的最后一排，孤单的身影，与周围的世界，有些格格不入。"
    "With a bitter smile, Xiao Yan turned around lonely and quietly returned to the last row of the team. His solitary figure seemed somewhat out of place with the surrounding world."
